{
  "id": "adv_main_01_11_02",
  "title": "星見編3章2話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_corridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4666666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 6.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 6.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……うん\n特に用がある訳じゃないんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… yeah.\nI don’t have anything in particular to talk about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……うん\nなんか、ごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… yeah.\nI just… want to say sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "何か謝るようなこと、あったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you do something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ううん……謝ることっていうか……\nちょっと変なことになっちゃって、っていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ no‚ I didn’t do anything wrong‚ exactly.\nThings just kinda got‚ you know‚ weird…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……だから、何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈さん、誕生日だったんだね、昨日……\nさっき、掲示板に書いてあった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was Mana’s birthday yesterday‚ right?\nSomeone wrote it on the message board.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……\nもう、あまり関係ないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very well…\nNot like it matters anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "…………ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "……ええと、私ね、別に麻奈さんの声に\n合わせようとか考えてる訳じゃなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ listen. I’m not exactly trying\nto imitate Mana’s voice or anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "自然と歌っているというか……\nその……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just sing naturally‚ I guess.\nIt’s‚ er…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そのこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh. Is that all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私は特に気にしてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not particularly bothered by it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "本当？　でも……お姉さんの声に似てるの\n嫌じゃないかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? But… I thought you might be mad\nthat my voice sounds like your sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why ever not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "だって……私は、麻奈さんじゃないし……\nそれに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… because I’m not Mana.\nNot to mention…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、お姉さんのために\nアイドルになったんじゃないのかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ isn’t your sister\nthe reason you became an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、それだけじゃないのは分かるよ\nけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I know that’s not the only reason.\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。グランプリの決勝で歌えなかった\nお姉ちゃんにかわって自分が歌いたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. My sister couldn’t sing at the Grand Prix finals.\nSo I want to sing in her place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "……そういう気持ちは、正直ある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do have those feelings. That’s the truth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、さくらの声がお姉ちゃんに似ているのは\nそれとは別の話でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But your voice sounding like my sister’s voice…\nThat’s unrelated‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんのことは、私とお姉ちゃんの問題\nさくらは関係ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Any issues I have with my sister are between her and me.\nIt’s nothing to do with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ、それで気を遣われる方が嫌",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In fact‚ I’d rather you not concern yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "だから、あなたはそんなこと気にしないで\n自由に歌って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you needn’t worry about it.\nJust sing freely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "…………うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（俺はその様子をこっそり盗み見しながら）\n（これからどうしたらいいのか考えていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As I quietly eavesdrop on them‚)\n(I think about how we should take things from here.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_shed-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 127.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 128.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 128.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
